      public Camp createCamp(String name, String start, String end, String endReg, String users, String locationStr, int slots, int commSlots, String desc, Staff staffIC)
      A Camp created by the Staff with the given attributes.
      Parameters:
      name - The Camp's name.
      start - The Camp's starting date.
      end - The Camp's ending date.
      endReg - The Camp's registration deadline.
      users - The User groups the Camp is open to.
      locationStr - The Camp's location.
      slots - The number of attendee slots the Camp has.
      commSlots - The number of Camp Committee slots the Camp has.
      desc - The Camp's description.
      staffIC - This Staff.
      Returns:
      The created Camp.
